Print the count of the occurrences of positive integers, negative integers, and zeroes in the given array.
Input Format
The first line of the input contains an integer N - size of the array, second line of input contains an array elements of the array.n=int(input())
===*===
pos=neg=zeros=0
a=list(map(int,input().split()))
for i in a:
    if i==0:
        zeros+=1
    elif i<=0:
        neg+=1
    else:
        pos+=1
print(f"pos={pos} neg={neg} zeros={zeros}")
